OL,6,FNearly all top-tier councils plan to
OL,7,Fraise council tax by the maximum
OL,8,Fpermitted to avoid financial distress,
OL,9,Fnew analysis shows.
OL,11,FOf the 136 authorities which have
OL,12,Fdeclared their proposals, 128 (94%)
OL,13,Fare looking to increase bills in April
OL,14,Fby 4.99% ` the biggest amount allowed
OL,15,Fby the Government without having to
OL,16,Fhold a local referendum.
