OL,6,FThe County Councils Network (CCN),
OL,7,Fwhich released the figures, said
OL,8,Fresearch at the same time last year
OL,9,Fshowed 75% of councils intended to
OL,10,Fimpose the maximum rise.
OL,12,FIt added council tax decisions are
OL,13,Fdriven by the scale of the financial
OL,14,Fpressures authorities remain under,
OL,15,Fdespite the Government's recent
OL,16,Femergency #600 million injection.
