OL,3,CMaximum council tax rise in nearly all
OL,4,Careas, analysis finds
OL,6,FSam Corcoran, Labour leader of
OL,7,FCheshire East Council and CCN vice-
OL,8,Fchairman, said councils have to make
OL,9,F"some of their toughest decisions"
OL,10,Fbecause of increased costs and spikes
OL,11,Fin demand for social care services.
OL,13,FHe added that, while the additional
OL,14,Ffunding provided by the Government
OL,15,Fwould make a tangible difference and
OL,16,Fprotect services, the fragile state of
OL,17,Fcouncil finances means council tax
OL,18,Fbills had to rise to ensure
OL,19,Fsustainability.
