OL,4,Careas, analysis finds
OL,6,FSeventeen top-tier authorities are yet
OL,7,Fto declare their council tax
OL,8,Fintentions.
OL,10,FFour councils which have previously
OL,11,Fissued section 114 notices declaring
OL,12,Feffective bankruptcy ` Birmingham,
OL,13,FWoking, Slough and Thurrock ` have
OL,14,Fbeen given special dispensation by the
OL,15,FGovernment to raise council tax by 10%.
OL,17,FThe proposed increases overall mean
OL,18,Fthe average Band D household will face
OL,19,Fan increase of #103 over the year on
OL,20,Faverage.
